languages.text: "Что-то подсказывает мне, шерин, что мы опоздали на рандеву с Лорд-инквизитором. Сколь невежливо с его стороны сорваться с места, оставив вас в неведении относительно собственных планов..."
"Something tells me, shereen, that we've missed our engagement with the Lord Inquisitor. So terribly rude of him to have departed in such haste, leaving us to wonder what he is planning..."

languages.text: « J'ai l'impression que nous avons manqué notre rendez-vous avec le seigneur inquisiteur, shereen. C'est affreusement impoli de sa part de partir aussi précipitamment, sans nous donner la moindre indication de ce qu'il manigance... »
languages.original_text: "Something tells me, shereen, that we've missed our engagement with the Lord Inquisitor. So terribly rude of him to have departed in such haste, leaving us to wonder what he is planning..."

languages.text: "Irgendetwas sagt mir, Shereen, dass wir unsere Verabredung mit dem Großinquisitor verpasst haben. Wie schrecklich unhöflich von ihm, so überstürzt aufzubrechen und uns mutmaßen zu lassen, was er wohl vorhat ..."
languages.original_text: "Something tells me, shereen, that we've missed our engagement with the Lord Inquisitor. So terribly rude of him to have departed in such haste, leaving us to wonder what he is planning..."

languages.text: «Shereen, algo me dice que llegamos tarde al encuentro con el Lord Inquisidor. Es muy feo por su parte haberse marchado de forma tan apresurada, dejándonos con la duda de qué está planeando...».

languages.text: 「ピンときたよ、シャリーン。アタシ達はロード・インクィジターとの約束を逃したんだ。アイツがあんなにさっさとどこかへ行くなんてあまりにも無礼だし、何を計画しているのか疑っちゃうね…」
languages.original_text: "Something tells me, shereen, that we've missed our engagement with the Lord Inquisitor. So terribly rude of him to have departed in such haste, leaving us to wonder what he is planning..."

languages.text: “亲爱的，我总觉得咱们好像是错过了与大审判官的约会。他实在是太粗鲁了，走得那么匆忙，都不告诉咱们他到底在打什么算盘……”
